subject: RE: [junit] Please remove my address from list
msgSnippet: He s probably trying to unsubscribe from a different address than the one he used to subscribe.  If he can t get back to that address, it is up to the
messageBody:
He's probably trying to unsubscribe from a different address than the one he
used to subscribe. If he can't get back to that address, it is up to the
moderator to remove him.

-jason
